Make the Emercoin ID Application:
 - Log in to any Emercoin ID webserver with EMC SSL certificate at https://oauth.authorizer.io
 - Create the app
 - Use URI as https://YOUR_DRUPAL_HOSTNAME/user/emercoin-id-login/return


Plugin installation and configuration:
 - Copy folder 'modules' to the htdocs root folder
 - Log in to the admin dashboard
 - Activate the plugin at: Modules -> List -> Authentication / Emercoin ID -> Install
 - Configure the Emercoin ID plugin with all necessary params
 - Disable new users approving at: Configuration -> People / Account Settings -> Settings -> Registration and Cancellation:
     (*) Who can register account? -> Visitors
     (*) Uncheck the "Require email verification when a visitor creates an account"
   -> Save configuration

After that you can see the "Emercoin ID login" button at the login page at https://YOUR_DRUPAL_HOSTNAME/user
